            <li class="qa-set">
                <p class="q">My Santee has very unrealistic(or expensive) wishlist. What do I do?</p>
                <p class="a">That shouldn't stop a good Santa. Maybe time to follow your Santee on twitter or email & find out what he/she likes.</p>
            </li>
            <li class="qa-set">
                <p class="q">What should be the budget of the gift to my Santee?</p>
                <p class="a">A good Santee will never put the value on gifts. You can buy him/her anything which you think will make them happy. Just try not to go full lavish :P</p>
