            <li class="qa-set">
                <p class="q">What if I don't feel like giving gift to my Santee?</p>
                <p class="a">Would you really want to do that? Just imagine somewhere your Santee has given a gift to his/her Santee & excited to receive the same from you. Would you want to break their heart? But for any reason if you can't then we expect you to send an email to us & your santee informing the same. Failing to do so will get you blacklisted from future secretsantas</p>
